BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260531
DESCRIPTION:Stop met ons te fokken! (Stop messing/breeding us!) With this slogan and a decorated livestock trailer\, we are traveling across the Netherlands. We oppose the ever-growing animal suffering in our current agricultural and food system\, and the large-scale livestock industry behind it.\n\nActivist action tour against intensive livestock farming and the agro-industry. Participants travel with a decorated livestock truck\, engage with people in public spaces\, and raise awareness about animal suffering\, pollution\, and exploitation in the agricultural system. New participants are welcome and signup is required.\n\nLocation: Eindhoven\, Netherlands\nSignup: https://extinctionrebellion.nl/events/stop-met-ons-te-fokken-6/
LOCATION:Eindhoven\, Netherlands
SUMMARY:Stop met ons te fokken!
UID:d4b36eb3-d92a-4fee-820d-8459f3ee3af3@d4b3.org
URL:https://extinctionrebellion.nl/events/stop-met-ons-te-fokken-6/
END:VEVENT
